                <!-- Project Detail Content (for Project 2) -->
                <div id="project2Content" class="hidden">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Clinical Workflow Optimization - Detailed Case Study</h4>
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/700x400/a78bfa/ffffff?text=Detailed+Project+2+Image" alt="Detailed Project 2" class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-md">
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        This project focused on enhancing the efficiency of patient management and record-keeping within a busy clinical setting. My responsibilities included analyzing existing workflows, identifying bottlenecks, and implementing a new digital patient record system.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        **Challenges:** The clinic faced challenges with paper-based record keeping, leading to delays in patient processing and potential for data loss. Staff resistance to new technology was also a factor.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        **Solution:** I collaborated with the IT department and clinic staff to select and customize an electronic health record (EHR) system. I led training sessions for all clinical personnel and and created user-friendly guides to ensure a smooth transition.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        **Results:** The implementation of the new EHR system reduced average patient check-in and record retrieval times by **15%**. Data accuracy improved, and the clinic was able to process more patients per day, leading to increased patient satisfaction.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Skills applied: Workflow Analysis, EHR Implementation, Training & Development, Data Management.</p>
